    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 at MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB intended-use context as described in the Claim and Requirement documentation. Decision accepted by the credibility assessment team on 2026-04-19.",
